column5: Nice one Terry! Ill be lookiung for her and 4 freinds at the Simcoe open at the end of Oct.LOL
Beautiful Smallie Terry!
Fat Terry, nice dood.
Na, we passed right by it. Figured you fished it out.LOL
Very nice Bass Terry....  .....who does your ironing?...the crease on your sleeve is outstanding
Nice fish...looks like it would have gone for 6 lbs if it had a tail.
Nice, really nice smallie guys! When I read the post title, I would have bet that it was a big silver thing that goes Bahh, bah! LOL HH
You might be right.  I am going to give it another shot tomorrow evening to see if I can scare up a few more.
Great fish Terry. Where did you buy that shirt?? I gotta get me one just like it.
Thought I would start the suspense now. What a real nice fish.  It will be worth the wait.
What kind of fish was it???
It was caught on  a spinnerbait.
I dunno.... with Terry being the Photoshop King... his credibility is somewhat limited!   ... but I believe you Brian.
ill bet i know

well it doesn't look that big in the picture maybe I do need to touch it up a little bit but it did put up a great fight they didn't seem to be schooling just one here and one there I think all but one was caught on spinnerbait another great day on the water Thanks for the company Misfish lets do it again soon

Your right bud,your holding it all wrong.LOL They sure were on the spinner baits today.Nothing like watching them smack that bait. I could not believe it took me that long to get a tube bite.HAHA Whats with the water too? Man it was so cloudy and we have had nothing but calm waters for a week. That fish will be two pounds heavier come October.
Beauty of a fish.  Nice going Terry.
was it weighed?
No,but I would have to say,just tilting the 6 pound mark.
Very nice fish Terry!!!
That IS a big fish Terry! Congrats to you. Oh, and nice shirt too!
Nice bass Terry but i think we can do better next weekend  Rob
Beautiful hog     Congrats Terry
Very nice catch Terry and a few more pics would have been great
What a monster, way to go Terry  She's a beaut for sure.   And Roy's right, that is a nice top  Joey
dress for success................................LOL   and it works
What a pig!!! But the camera man should be fired!!! He missed the entire tail!!! When you catch monsters like that you should take a few pictures!!!
Beauty fish Terry, congrats !!!
Great fish Terry, congrats!  Must have felt like a freight train hammering that spinnerbait.
Bull__it!!  It looks BIG enough to me!!! Way to go Terry!!  :clapping:
Great catch Terry!  I've never caught a bass anywhere near that size...in fact, I think yours could eat my best for breakfast....
That fish is huge! Congrats, That must have been a rush!
hmmm.  Did you guys hit up my spot this morn?  lol!  I hope so.  That fish actually looks much darker than those from my spot so it might not be.  Congrats!!  Nice hawg!
